Flask Microservices with PostgreSQL & JWT (Windows)
Overview

Two microservices:
---------------------
Login Service – User registration & login (JWT).
Shopping Service – Products & cart management.

Setup (Windows)
-------------------
1. Login Service
cd login_service
python -m venv venv
venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
python app.py

Runs on port 5000
DB: logindb

2. Shopping Service
-----------------------
cd shopping_service
python -m venv venv
venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
python app.py

Runs on port 5001
DB: shoppingdb
